  <span id="freeText17974947892028350074" style="display:none">Anyone who loves <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/406575.The_Riddle_of_the_Sands" title="The Riddle of the Sands by Erskine Childers" rel="nofollow noopener">The Riddle of the Sands</a> by <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/230318.Erskine_Childers" title="Erskine Childers" rel="nofollow noopener">Erskine Childers</a> will love Sam Llewellyn's sequel. <br />Some of Childers' characters make a reappearance to join Llewellyn's hero in defeating the dastardly Hun. <br />Well written from the point of view of a working class professional yacht skipper of the time, and a tremendous twist at the end when you think that all is lost. </span>
